divs: Sighting DetailsTHIS IS THE FOUTH ATTEMPT TO WRITE MY STORY. FOR SOME REASON MY COMPUTER KEEPS ERASNG IT. ANYHOW I WAS COMING HOME FROM WORK , NOTICED LIGHT IN THE SKY. NOTICED IT WAS GETTING CLOSER AND LARGER. REALIZED IT WAS FOLLOWING ME. IT PASSED DIRECTLY OVER MY HEAD AT TREE TOP LEVEL. IT HAD RED AND WHITE LIGHTS ON IT. ITS BELLY WAS OF DIFFERNET DESIGNS AND THERE WAS NO SOUND. THE CIRCCULAR DISK WAS THE ONLY THING SPINNING ON THE CRAFT. I WOULD TELL YOU MORE BUT THIS COMPUTER IS ACTING UP. ALSO I HAVE HAD TWO DREAMS THAT I WAS ABOARD A SPACE CRAFT, THEY TOLD ME WHY THEY COME AND SHOWED ME THE CRAFT.red and white lights
